        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 29a–g. Orseolia javanica: a, gall on Imperata cylindrica (arrow indicates one of two galls; Fig. II-5 of DvLR & DvL (1926)); b, male terminalia; c, 12th male flagellomere; d, 3rd female flagellomere; e, 12th female flagellomere; f, 3rd female flagellomere; g, male terminalia (dorsal). Figs b–e from Kieffer & DvLR (1910) depicting types (now lost), Figs. f, g from Gagné (1985) of specimens in BMNH." ;
